  "title": "Trainee Air Hub Lead - Baggage",
  "description": "<p><strong>​</strong>Our client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit a Trainee Air Hub Lead - Baggage.<strong> </strong>This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Trainee Air Hub Lead - Baggage</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>Supervise baggage operations to ensure baggage are dispatched to aircraft in a timely manner as per airlines' requirements or stipulations by the aviation authority.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>• Diploma in any discipline</p>\n<p>• Comfortable with shift work</p>\n<p>• Physically Fit</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n <br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
